OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government agency
OL,7,FNatureScot has been consulting on
OL,8,Fwhether Galloway should be designated
OL,9,FScotland's third national park.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Government announced on
OL,12,F29 May 2025 that the plans had been
OL,13,Fscrapped.
OL,15,FSpeaking in Holyrood this afternoon
OL,16,F(29 May 2025), Rural Affairs Secretary
OL,17,FMairi Gougeon MSP said the government
OL,18,Fhad "made the decision not to proceed
OL,19,Fwith the designation of a new national
OL,20,Fpark for Galloway and Ayrshire".
