OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,FShe said the government had "weighed
OL,7,Fup the arguments for and against" the
OL,8,Fproposal, adding that the public
OL,9,Fconsultation had seen 54% of
OL,10,Frespondents outline their opposition,
OL,11,Fwhile 42% were in favour.
OL,13,FHere are some of the arguments from
OL,14,Fthose on both sides of the debate.
OL,16,FSusan Dixon runs self-catering holiday
OL,17,Faccommodation at Carsethorn.
OL,19,F"I think it would bring more visitors
OL,20,Fto the area, which is really needed,"
OL,21,Fshe said.
