OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,F"It's a lovely area all year round.
OL,7,FWhen I did B&B people used to say I've
OL,8,Fnever visited this corner of Scotland
OL,9,Fbefore, they've all been to the
OL,10,FHighlands and Islands and Edinburgh
OL,11,Fand Stirling, but they'd not been here
OL,12,Fand they were really pleasantly
OL,13,Fsurprised at how beautiful it was and
OL,14,Fthey wanted to come back."
OL,16,FSteve Norris is the former editor of
OL,17,Fthe Galloway Gazette and an SNP
OL,18,Fcampaigner.
