OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,F"I've seen over the decades a slow and
OL,7,Fperceptible decline in Galloway and
OL,8,Fit's ongoing," he said.
OL,10,F"School rolls are falling, and we need
OL,11,Fto do something to turn around our
OL,12,Feconomy. The number of pubs,
OL,13,Fhospitality businesses, restaurants
OL,14,Fand so on that have closed down in
OL,15,FGalloway in the last 30 or 40 years
OL,16,Fthere's dozens, perhaps hundreds of
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
