OL,3,CGalloway National Park: What were the
OL,4,Carguments for and against?
OL,6,FColin Ferguson is a farmer and branch
OL,7,Fchair of the Wigtownshire NFUS.
OL,9,F"There's absolutely no doubt this area
OL,10,Fneeds employment, it needs jobs, it
OL,11,Fneeds industry, it needs businesses to
OL,12,Fwant to come here," he said.
